"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"打开<https://chainlist.org/>\\n\\n在上方搜索框输入 smart bitcoin，会跳出两个结果，一个是smartbch的主网，一个是测试网 。看币代码就可以区分，主网的币代码是BCH，测试网是BCHT。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YF0-9Zzz7t6wh3f6dfE1r.png?height=475&width=793)\\n\\n点击主网结果的那个”add to metamask“\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JLp3RyHWYEt4nY7hUchV2.png?height=729&width=481)\\n\\n点击”approve“\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pPjoGltjXOvi-LKEnz-Pi.png?height=783&width=544)\\n\\n再点”switch network“\\n\\n然后就完成了，你的metamask钱包已经自动保存了smartbch的配置参数，并且自动切换到smartbch主网，可以开始正常使用了。\",\"timestamp\":1638284054,\"title\":\"小狐狸钱包Metamask创建教程\"},\"digest\":\"ZRU1s8xSElI4Qo7KrppAfG_iLfthK-8_lrO1SnmQ_Zg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe9976bB7a8cB79101dCa249285fd33C1daC88AA1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"7U7jSuMk0YpVuBtN2g6aUo00Nsu1Oep7YUe0l-m2geE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"oy09UIjqn4CuGlbL3iJigO4yZ7sGna5Eoc8pYvgWbcY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"FD5mqMK2mWXIKa-9oSnQV6QjZOx3scmZxSXEgnwV5bKXQ2k8Hr2mLKBmMd2L4NTH6T7mCCjzwWM4rEpDa5wX4Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb14e977881f02997a9d863031c22181847bd109ea1bcf4be3fd8ff3a81002aef75f9681e2894017823a924b71538a66cd83bb3f001d814db41bcd412fa0769a21b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"7U7jSuMk0YpVuBtN2g6aUo00Nsu1Oep7YUe0l-m2geE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"oy09UIjqn4CuGlbL3iJigO4yZ7sGna5Eoc8pYvgWbcY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ZRU1s8xSElI4Qo7KrppAfG_iLfthK-8_lrO1SnmQ_Zg\"}"